Source: fbsql
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/dsc-chiba-u/FbSQL

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-fbsql
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-fbsql
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION-plr (>= 8.4.0)
Description: Formula-based statistical modeling in SQL for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 FbSQL provides a relation-oriented statistical modeling DSL. It fits
 Gaussian and binomial generalized linear models through PL/R and scores
 relations from the resulting model relation.
